    "shortDescription": "<p>A wavering red ray projects from your finger. You must succeed on a ranged touch attack with the ray to hit your target.</p><p>The ray inflicts 1d4 points of nonlethal damage, causing the target to suffer from heatstroke as its body temperature dramatically increases. Except as noted above, this spell otherwise functions as <i>ray of exhaustion</i>.</p><p>Characters wearing heavy clothing or armor of any sort take a -4 penalty on their saves.</p>"
